{
    "chapterId": "Act01_Chapter02_Trial",
    "lines": [
        {
            "id": "line_2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "我们得尝试还原案发过程，还记得C的死因和验尸结果吗",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "嗯...几乎所有条件都指向病发致死而非他杀。线索太有限了为什么不全部探索完再庭审？",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_4",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "规定就是规定。规定又不是我定的。",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长2",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_5",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "好吧假设C有整理内务的习惯，那么一切都说的通了：C晚上躺在床上时感到了身体异样，此时他以无力呼救，于是决定安静的迎接死亡",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_6",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "等等，如果是病发有一个疑点无法解释",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_7",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "抓痕",
                "refute_1_success",
                "refute_1_fail"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "refute_1_fail",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "总而言之就是这样，还有别的可能",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_8_jump",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["line_9"]
        },
        {
            "id": "refute_1_success",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "假如是病发墙角的抓痕只可能是其他人留下的，那这个人是谁？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_9",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "可以把他赶出去吗，或者说你就是凶手所以才要扰乱我们的思路？",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_10",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "直接投票吧 我都看出来了",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_11",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "发言前还请三思",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_12",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "所以问题是C死前到底接触了什么，房间里的抓痕又是谁留下的",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_13",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "或者换个思路上述说明C死亡期间有与他人接触。但是我在巡逻的时候没有看见别人，那就只能说明一点——C是在门禁前或是门禁后被杀害的",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_14",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "嗯，确定下时间就好办了，大家晚上有出房间过吗",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_15",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "我先说吧，我没出去过",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_16",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "不知道，喝完剩下的酒我倒头就睡了",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_17",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "门禁前去过一次厕所，很快就回来了",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_18",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "播报完后，我一直待在办公室里。门禁后才去的巡逻",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长2",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_19",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "ShowChoice",
            "parameters": [
                "A|branch_a_start",
                "B|branch_b_start",
                "典狱长|branch_w_start"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_a_start",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "不，你说的跟在你房间里找到的线索有出入，那就是：",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_20",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "酒瓶",
                "branch_a_success",
                "branch_a_fail"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_a_success",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "这瓶崭新的酒，你怎么解释",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_21",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "这...这是 好吧这是我从C房间里抢的这本来是说好给我的但这孙子耍赖，我拿了酒就走了",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_22",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "刚刚还是另一套说法的谁又能保证你这次说的又是真的",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_23",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["A", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_24",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_a_fail",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "这点，你怎么解释",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_25",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "所以这前后有什么关联？你想再被我揍一顿吗？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_26",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_27",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_start",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你说的与某个人的说辞存在矛盾",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_28",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你是说你在外面的期间既没有看见A也没看见A口中的“C”吗？这恐怕不对吧",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_29",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "有没有可能是A在撒谎呢，他那个点根本不在外面",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_30",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "老子可不屑干这种事！",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_31",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "不他不可能撒谎，因为",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_32",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "带血的绷带",
                "branch_b_success",
                "branch_b_fail"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_success",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "因为他门禁前跟我打了一场才回去，所以只可能是\n你在说谎",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_33",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["B", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_34",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_fail",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "呃呃呃，总之就是这个原因",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_35_fail",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "这么着急将矛头指向别人，是向掩饰真相吗？",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_36",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_37",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_w_start",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "典狱长，你巡逻的时候确保所有罪犯都在房间里吗",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_38",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "是的，全部确认后我才离开",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_39",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "嗯，但是你没确认躺在房间里的就是本人",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_40",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "能证明这一点的就是：",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_41",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "床",
                "branch_w_success",
                "branch_w_fail"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_w_success",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你不可能没发现C奇怪的死状，这说明C只可能在门禁前死的不然没法解释夜里C一点动静都没有就被他杀了。\n凶手先杀了C，自己在伪人化进入C的房间装作C正常躺在床上。\n最后等巡逻结束后再用了某种方式将C运回了房间，摆出奇怪的姿势。\n或者说你在有意隐瞒什么，我可以这么理解吗",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_42",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "这样确实可以推出C的具体死亡时间。不过至于你的猜想，无稽之谈",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长2",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_43",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "但你可得为你说过的话负责哦长官",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_44",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["典狱长", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_45",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_w_fail",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "没错，就是这一点可以证明",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_46",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "你有权保持沉默，但是你所说的每句话将成为呈堂证供",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长2",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_47",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_48",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "trial_end",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "",
            "text": "进入投票阶段，会场再次陷入死一样的寂静",
            "portrait": "null",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_50",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "记录完成，下一轮。",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_51",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "LoadScene"
        }
    ]
}